    atk: 0
    def: 2000
    flavor: "[ Pendulum Effect ] If you have an 'Igknight' card in your other Pendulum Zone: You can destroy both cards in your Pendulum Zones, and if you do, add 1 FIRE Warrior-Type monster from your Deck or Graveyard to your hand. ---------------------------------------- [ Flavor Text ] The cold steel armor of this young squire cannot hide the keen, burning mind contained within."

    raw_effect "Effect 1" {
